            LINK</a>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text style="font-size: 14px" align="justify">
          Webpage: <a href="https://rmiteduau.sharepoint.com/sites/SCLDepartment/SitePages/Home.aspx" style="color: #3498DB; text-decoration: none;">
            LINK</a>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text style="font-size: 14px" align="justify">
          In the current Team, there are three channels which can be updated/modified based on the colleagues feedback:
          <ul>
            <li>
              <b>General:</b> For general research-oriented discussions and/or seeking colleagues<span>&#39;</span> feedback.
            </li>
            <li>
              <b>Events:</b> The details of external and internal events are posted to this channel.
            </li>
            <li>
              <b>News Chain:</b> The most recent and interesting supply chain news are posted here. To cover the broad range of our department<span>&#39;</span>s research interest and expertise, it is greatly appreciated, if colleagues could send me a link to the news that they wish to be published in this channel.
            </li>
